Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(460,160)}2話  我…想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心目中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拭去你的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  淚水拭去後那臉頰的柔軟觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻無從得知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笑容我想畫得更溫馨一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人手好像不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等這個完工後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼「啊  是嗎」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在裝什麼酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲  我在做下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還在記帳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不一起吃掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒法收拾餐具了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話不是這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她幫我們做了不少家務了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是站在那孩子一邊的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個地方有位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能收集你的眼淚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  我會把那些眼淚做成首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾在樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的…淚之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  已經不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰發明的啊  引體向上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  比呂美  真令人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好慢啊  都落後我好幾圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼那麼有體力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鍛煉的方式不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  你太色了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是大叔的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那纏住少女雪白大腿的粘乎乎的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被你那纏人的視線絆倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼胡話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯淺同學真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就是那種真正的優等生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也不自高自大  很完美不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎  你們明明住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會和她一起上學  偷看她換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她對我說「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴小愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便看人家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在取雞的餌料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是天空的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子明明想飛上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被關在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會取最高地方的食物給它的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼飛上天空  雞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不給這隻雞吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這孩子是只不想飛的雞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你也是和這只是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想飛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  頭一次和我說話的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知道我的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唾沫會飛出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  我覺得我也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很能飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你頭腦好像很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我詛咒你會遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那傢伙是A班的石動乃繪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒怎麼見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年才搬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挺可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻有著很多不妙的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說會和地底人發短信之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一吹口哨就能召喚出粉紅色的大象之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  如果是那傢伙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被她詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪必殺奧義  召喚悲劇的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說有人被她說「詛咒你那個變小」後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真變成沒用的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工頭有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的熟人死後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人的女兒比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去年由我家領養了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我從小學起就是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美一直都很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很在意她那張笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我詛咒你會遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哀聲歎氣會變得不幸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小愛你也想詛咒別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是自己喜歡才跳什麼舞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是被賦予重望的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊  跳得一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全不可能成為麥屋舞的當家花旦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想生在那種家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只比我大一歲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年也差很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這到處爬來爬去的嬰兒也很能說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台詞等你把腳底下的啤酒箱拿走再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店舖關門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真一郎  你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家那邊的幫忙完事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要燒著喉嚨的那種來雙倍濃度的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  是可樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  拿酒來喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟打攪你們也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  用不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  上衣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我擅自看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該道歉的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…  為什麼你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一般來說都是那種反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美的確寄住在我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  她一直都很低聲下氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是東京的出版社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都瞞著爸爸做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自拆封了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  嗯  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得擅自拆封不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真可是這仲上家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎就是真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仲上家沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我詛咒你會遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字不是「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你幫我把那個取消掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我變得不幸的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美極了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著那麼誇獎我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不挺能飛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子  乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雷轟丸也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻雞的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飛不了的那只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都已經決定好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸貓幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是這樣的吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我詛咒你會遇到不幸」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒別人是把雙刃劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  雷轟丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯  都是因為鑽牛角尖的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很疼愛它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很傷心  非常地非常地傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把眼淚送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著一個使命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須取回眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想讓我代替雷轟丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想做什麼…
